Packages 
Package Description
code
This package contains all model classes of the code representation.
codetest
Contains the main converter class and TemporaryModel as a temporary storage of converted elements.
codetest.converters
Contains the actual converter classes with their static methods
core
Contains the main application class Core
core.options
Contains class processing the command line arguments passed in Core
inputmdxml
Contains the main converter class which calls the actual converter classes
inputmdxml.converter.element
Contains converter classes converting PackagedElements and their child elements to UmlElements
inputmdxml.converter.relationship
Contains converter classes converting PackagedElements and their child elements to UmlRelationships
inputmdxml.temporary
Contains auxiliary elements to store temporary conversion results
junit
Contains all model classes of the junit representation, used to fill the mustache template for test generation.
mdxml
This package contains all model classes of the MDXML representation.
outputjunit
Contains the main converter class and TemporaryModel as a temporary storage of converted elements.
outputjunit.converter
Contains converter classes converting the TestRepresentation to the JunitRepresentation
outputjunit.files
Contains classes creating files and directories for the test files
test
This package contains classes determining the test file structure.
Each TestClass contains a ClassUnderTest object representing the test cases.
test.converterinterface
This package provides an interface for output converters.
test.testobjects
This package provides classes representing the test cases to be tested.
They are grouped in a ClassUnderTest which is assigned to a TestClass.
uml
This package contains all model classes of the UML representation.
uml.converterinterface
This package provides interfaces for an input representation converter and the input representation.
umlcode
Contains the main converter class and TemporaryModel as a temporary storage of converted elements.
umlcode.converter.element
Contains converter classes for UmlElements and UmlPackages
umlcode.converter.relationship
Contains converter classes for UmlRelationships to map supplier and client CodeElements of interface realizations and generalizations to each other.
